{"tid":977434,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"珠海撿「炮彈果」如臨大敵放防爆箱","createTime":"2019-01-11T07:39:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-13T03:24:29.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"70eaa6a3bd81e27ff7d108bcad4dccc011b79846","tid":977434,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T07:39:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20190111/20588402\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190111%2F20588402&d=3hh%2BA0qHVMPSzoNK472kftibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=b5296a41\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190111%2F20588402&h=547dfcc1\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20190111/20588402</a><br />\n<br />\n2019年01月11日 <br />\n<br />\n珠海撿「炮彈果」如臨大敵放防爆箱<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190111/large/a1904a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190111%2Flarge%2Fa1904a.gif&h=121bbb75&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n珠海拱北口岸近日在旅客的行李內，查到一顆名為「炮彈果」的球狀果實（圖）。內媒《廣州日報》稱，該果實號稱世上「最危險的水果」，受外力衝擊會爆炸，威力近乎小型手榴彈，關員將其存放到防爆箱中。但內地科普雜誌《博物雜誌》澄清，指炮彈果根本爆不了，只是長得像古代的炮彈。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n專家指不會爆<br />\n<br />\n珠海拱北口岸海關稱，一名旅客的行李篋接受X光機檢查時，圖像顯示內藏有一個尺寸較大的球狀物體，引起海關關員注意，隨後發現是一顆名為「炮彈果」的球狀果實，外表呈茶褐色，重約3.8公斤。旅客聲稱，果實由新加坡好友所贈，準備帶入境與家人分享。旅客因未申報且無檢疫審批手續，被關員扣查果實及銷毀。<br />\n<br />\n《廣州日報》報道，炮彈果受到一定外力衝擊時會爆炸，威力近乎小型手榴彈。然而，報道立即遭反駁，《博物雜誌》在官微解釋，炮彈果在東南亞不少國家是常見水果，「根本就爆不了，只是長得像古代的炮彈才叫這名字」。《博物》又指，炮彈果很好看，泰國多種在寺廟門口。<br />\n<br />\n《廣州日報》/新浪微博  <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n捲2.54億被台通緝　貴婦奈奈逃加國尋庇護<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n港澳台居民內地任教　須擁護中共"},{"pid":"649e345c251abc7f0175e9d1c9658fea9797ca22","tid":977434,"uid":2521,"like":54,"dislike":0,"score":54,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T07:42:42.000Z","msg":"大陸人都覺得，生果會爆係好正常<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50ec9a9c71c2cea89c179337ff3c8d1f6eb8d812","tid":977434,"uid":212729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T08:18:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b6558ddbe5e487e7e9f6e34a7c10322d7fd4be68","tid":977434,"uid":155682,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T08:21:43.000Z","msg":"本身係東南亞係唔會，但入到大陸就有機會會爆。"},{"pid":"c1d8fd58c4bfa4deb0b842347fed37fb7f707911","tid":977434,"uid":13467,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"b6558ddbe5e487e7e9f6e34a7c10322d7fd4be68","tid":977434,"uid":155682,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T08:21:43.000Z","msg":"本身係東南亞係唔會，但入到大陸就有機會會爆。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T08:25:13.000Z","msg":"借口黎姐<br />\n轉個頭班海關食埋啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c188b510517c276c10cf2f4a6bdea7580e0211a","tid":977434,"uid":108467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T08:29:21.000Z","msg":"港澳台居民內地任教　須擁護中共<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d140bbc741ac989095ed556bedaf3a48e3e568a1","tid":977434,"uid":35598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T08:32:54.000Z","msg":"原來有炮彈果呢樣嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f7d1caf66165790a79a30f8db1470ddd18d1d7d","tid":977434,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1c188b510517c276c10cf2f4a6bdea7580e0211a","tid":977434,"uid":108467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T08:29:21.000Z","msg":"港澳台居民內地任教　須擁護中共<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T08:33:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c20678c6a021f17ea9f23b697d1b6ba26456651d","tid":977434,"uid":98966,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":